        <name>ocpp_user_notify_callback_t</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Asynchronous event notification callback registered by the application. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>advised callback should not be hold for longer time to unblock the ocpp protocol stack/lib.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
